The problem is in the join column definition.

Current:

    @JoinColumn(name = &quot;USER_UUID&quot;, referencedColumnName = &quot;USER_UUID&quot;)

Should be probably:

    @JoinColumn(name = &quot;USER_ID&quot;, referencedColumnName = &quot;USER_ID&quot;)

Alternatively you can create a column USER_UUID in the CONTACTS table.

